@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@attachmentId = att-replace-after-upload
@localFile = /Users/sean/Document/demo-mfundtable.png
@localImage = /Users/sean/Desktop/id-card.png
@localMarkdown = /Users/sean/Desktop/policy.md
@localPdf = /Users/sean/Desktop/policy.pdf

### 1. Upload local text attachment only
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachments
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="id-card.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< {{localFile}}
--AgentHubBoundary--

### 2. Upload inline text attachment only
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachments
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="id-card.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

居民身份证 姓名 张三 公民身份号码 110101200901011234 出生日期 2009-01-01
--AgentHubBoundary--

### 3. Analyze existing attachment through business API
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachment-analysis/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "att-business-001",
  "userId": "attachment-reviewer",
  "attachmentId": "{{attachmentId}}"
}

### 4. Upload local text attachment and analyze in one request
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachment-analysis/analyze-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

attachment-reviewer
--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="id-card.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< {{localFile}}
--AgentHubBoundary--

### 5. Upload inline text and analyze in one request
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachment-analysis/analyze-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

attachment-reviewer
--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="id-card.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

居民身份证 姓名 李四 公民身份号码 110101199901011234 出生日期 1999-01-01
--AgentHubBoundary--

### 6. Upload image mock and analyze in one request
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachment-analysis/analyze-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

attachment-reviewer
--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="id-card.png"
Content-Type: image/png

居民身份证 姓名 赵六 公民身份号码 110101200901011234 出生日期 2009-01-01
--AgentHubBoundary--

### 7. Upload local image and analyze through MiMo
# Start with:
# mvn -pl agent-document-processing spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=mimo
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachment-analysis/analyze-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

attachment-reviewer
--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="id-card.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< {{localImage}}
--AgentHubBoundary--

### 8. Analyze through AgentHub generic chat API
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "att-chat-001",
  "userId": "attachment-reviewer",
  "message": "请分析附件 {{attachmentId}}"
}

### 9. Permission denied example
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachment-analysis/analyze-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

u001
--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="contract.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

合同 甲方 A 公司 乙方 B 公司
--AgentHubBoundary--

### 10. Normal chat should not trigger attachment tools
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "att-chat-normal",
  "userId": "attachment-reviewer",
  "message": "请介绍一下智能附件分析"
}

### 11. Upload inline Markdown and extract outline
POST {{baseUrl}}/attachment-analysis/outline-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AgentHubBoundary

--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

attachment-reviewer
--AgentHubBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="policy.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

# 招生政策解读
## 报名条件
考生需要关注报名时间、资格审核和材料提交要求。
## 录取重点
重点关注专业组、选科要求、往年位次和风险兜底方案。
--AgentHubBoundary--

